---
title: Incident Response — escalation and self-loop polling
---

@theme clean
@direction TB

#start Start
  Assess all intel sources
  #decision Is there an event requiring police?
    -> yes: Call Police
    -> no: Monitor until resolved
  Call Police
  #decision Have they arrived?
    -> yes: Monitor until resolved
    -> no: Have they arrived?
  Monitor until resolved
  #decision Resolved?
    -> yes: #end Done
    -> no: Monitor until resolved
